NG0859:1: rtogs pa'i ye shes ro yi gter gyur chos kun de kho na nyid kyi //
NG0859:2: phyag rgyas btabs pas gnyis su mi phyed bsam gtan
NG0859:3: pha rol phyin gyur cig 46/ dngos por 'dzin pa'i
NG0859:4: tshang tshing kun 'dral chos nyid sgrib med gcer mthong
NG0859:5: bas // sgro 'dogs skur 'debs mtha' gnyis las rgyal 'jig rten gsum na dpa' gcig pa'i //
NG0859:6: gzungs dang spobs pa rgyun chad med pas sangs rgyas chos mdzod mchog bzung nas //
NG0859:7: mi snang rnams la sgron me spor byed shes rab
NG0859:8: pha rol phyin gyur cig 47/ ji snyed sems kyi
NG0859:9: 'jug pa de snyed skad cig rer yangs 'byams klas
NG0859:10: pa'i // re ba'i lag pa 'bras bus lci byed dag pa'i shel la tshon tshogs bzhin //
NG0859:11: gang blos mi gtong byang chub mchog tu nges par 'gyur ba de lta bu'i //
NG0859:12: bdud rtsi'i bgo skal rim par sbyin pa'i thabs mkhas
NG0859:13: pha rol phyin gyur cig /48 / gang gi snying
NG0859:14: stobs gzhig par rab dka' rnam par rgyal ba'i mtshan
NG0859:15: ma yis // yid srub longs spyod stongs pa'i gnas bkod mtha' dag myang 'das lam gzung bar //
NG0859:16: gzhan 'phrul bdag pos rtse gcig bsgrims pa'i dpung dang mtshon cha'i sbyor bas na //
NG0859:17: brdzi bar mi nus sangs rgyas chos kun stobs kyi
NG0859:18: pha rol phyin gyur cig / phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten
NG0859:19: sgrol ma rnams drung nam mkha'i mthas gtugs sems can
NG0859:20: rnams // ma lus sgrol phyir snying stobs go cha zhum pa med par rab 'gos shing *//
NG0859:21: zab cing rgya che'i 'phang rtsal la goms byang chub mchog gi sgyu thabs che //
NG0859:22: smon lam rgya mtsho'i pha rol phyin pas sems can
NG0859:23: khams rnams spyod gyur cig 50/ chos rnams kun la
NG0859:24: rnam par mi rtog rtog bral nam mkha'i mtshan nyid
NG0859:25: can // brtag par mi nus shes bya kun la ro mnyam yul dang yul can dang *//
NG0859:26: gcig dang du mar rnam par mi rtog dri med yang dag don du mthong *//
NG0859:27: so so rang gi rig bya 'od gsal ye shes
NG0859:28: pha rol phyin brnyes shog 51/ skye nas skye bar
NG0859:29: legs pa'i phyogs su gegs rnams gnas par ma gyur
NG0859:30: pas // bde ba can sogs dag pa'i zhing du rgyal ba'i myu gu gzhon nu'i tshul //
NG0859:31: rgyal ba rnams drung gus pas rab bsnyen sangs rgyas zhing sbyangs sems can gyi //
NG0859:32: khams rnams rgya mtsho rab tu sgrol ba'i spyod pa rgya mtsho mthar phyir shog 52/
NG0859:33: la lar gser gyi 'khor lo mdun 'gro brgya byin theg pa'i nor bu sogs //
NG0859:34: rin chen bdun gyis mdun du bdar bas rgya mtsho'i mthar thug sa chen po //
NG0859:35: mtshon dang g.yul gyis bda' ba med cing sngo ba med par rab phabs nas //
NG0859:36: chos ldan rgyal po'i chos kyi srid kyi bsam kun
NG0859:37: rdzogs par byed gyur cig 53 / la lar nags
NG0859:38: su rtsa yi spyil bur ku sha'i gdan dang 'bras
NG0859:39: bu'i zas // chu gtsar btung ba shin shun gos gyon rnal 'byor 'ba' zhig la @#//
NG0859:41: la lar khengs bral slong mos 'tsho zhing phyag dar khrod pa'i gos kyis mdzes //
NG0859:42: sems ni rab grol zhi ba'i gzugs kyis skye dgu'i
NG0859:43: 'dod pa 'jo gyur cig 54 / rang bzhin gnas
NG0859:44: rigs de bzhin nyid dbyings ngo bor spang pa mkha'
NG0859:45: lta bur // glo bur med snang sgrib gnyis sprin tshogs myur bde'i lam gyis yongs sbyangs te //
NG0859:46: bral smin yon tan bye ba'i 'od 'bar sku bzhi'i bdag nyid nyin mor byed //
NG0859:47: dka' ba med par mngon du byed las rnam rol
NG0859:48: zer brgya spro gyur cig 55/ mtho ris nas 'phos
NG0859:49: gzigs pa lngas gzigs yum gyi lhums su zhugs pa
NG0859:50: dang *// dga' ba'i tshal bltams gzhon nu'i rol rtsed nges par 'byung dang dka' thub dang *//
NG0859:51: byang chub snying por mngon sangs rgyas dang rim gsum chos 'khor bskor la sogs //
NG0859:52: rmad byung mdzad pas srid mtshor byings pa'i sems can
NG0859:53: ma lus sgrol gyur cig 56/ grags pa'i mtshan ma
NG0859:54: yid 'ong gyur pa mu tig phreng ba ltar dkar
NG0859:55: bas // phyogs kyi 'khor lo nges par brgal ba'i gsung rab glegs bam rgyas pa'i ma //
NG0859:56: rin thang bral ba'i rin chen gyis gtams nor bu'i shing rta bkram 'dra ba //
NG0859:57: sa gsum skye dgu'i mchod sdong gcig pur dus kyi
NG0859:58: mthar yang nyams med shog 57/ gang gi mthu yis
NG0859:59: 'jig rten kun tu dge legs snang ba 'byams klas
NG0859:60: pa'i // rnal grol mchog gi 'dzum rlab phye bas 'khor mun pha mthar snyil byed cing *//
NG0859:61: bsod nams ye shes gzugs brnyan brgya yi 'bras bu bdag nyid 'byor gyur pa'i //
NG0859:62: yon tan mtha' yas mi zad 'jo byed ko bi
NG0859:63: da ra ltar gyur cig 58 / bsod nams nas
NG0859:64: 'di 'bad pas bsgrubs la lus ngag yid kyi rtsol
NG0859:65: ba yis // dngos brgyud 'brel ba'i skye dgu ma lus sdug bsngal rgyu bcas mthar gyur nas //
NG0859:66: zhi bde'i gnas su rgyal sras rnams dang lhan cig
NG0859:67: byang chub spyod mchog gi / rol rtsed du mas
NG0859:68: rnam mkhyen grong du phyir mi ldog par 'gro gyur
NG0859:69: cig 59/ bdag 'dra dman pa'ang legs par gsung pa
NG0859:70: thos pa'i bdud rtsis rab ngoms shing *//
NG0859:71: bsam pas ro gzhib bsgom pa'i bcud kyis byang chub lang tsho rab smin pas //
NG0859:72: lus can yongs kyi nyer 'tsho'i gzhir gyur thabs tshul du mas sman bgyid cing *//
NG0859:73: rgyal bstan rdzogs pa'i shing rtar gyur nas bstan la
NG0859:74: bya ba byed gyur cig 60 / lhag bsam dag
NG0859:75: pa'i sa gzhir legs smin smon lam gser gyi snye
NG0859:76: ma'i tshal // shin tu sdug pa dri ma'i tshogs kyis gzhan yang nog par ma gyur pa //
NG0859:77: sgrib med gzigs pa'i 'phags chen rnams kyi smon lam rgya che'i phyogs bslan te //
NG0859:78: de dag bzhed pa'i lhag ma ma lus de ring bdag gis skong nus shog 61/
NG0859:79: sna tshogs chos kun gnyis su ma brtags chos kyi dbyings su ro mnyam @#//
NG0859:80: nyid du bden par gyur pa'i bden pa dang *//
NG0859:81: gang zhig rtogs dang gang gis rtogs byed zag bral
NG0859:82: lam bden 'dus ma byas chos legs par gsungs pa'i
NG0859:83: bden pa dang *// bden pas mthar byas srid las
NG0859:84: rnam grol 'gog pa la gnas rdul bral zhi gyur
NG0859:85: 'phags pa rnams kyi bden mchog gis //
NG0859:86: 'di na de ring ji ltar smon pa'i don rnams
NG0859:87: ma lus yongs su rdzogs pa'i dge legs chen po
NG0859:88: 'byung gyur cig 62/ bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa
NG0859:89: rin po che'i snying po rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde
NG0859:90: snod rdo rje theg pa las snga 'gyur rgyud sde
NG0859:91: rin po che'i rtogs pa brjod pa /
NG0859:92: lha'i rnga bo che lta bu'i gtams las legs byas
NG0859:93: rgya chen po bskrun pa'i phan yon bsngo smon dang
NG0859:94: bcas legs par bshad pa'i skabs te lnga pa'o ///
NG0859:95: / de ltar bde bar gshegs pa'i gsung rab thams
NG0859:96: cad kyi snying po rdo rje theg pa snga 'gyur
NG0859:97: rgyud 'bum rin po che'i rtogs pa brjod pa deng
NG0859:98: sang gangs ri'i ljongs 'dir ji tsam snyed pa glegs
NG0859:99: bam zad mi shes pa'i phyi mor bsgrub pa'i tshul
NG0859:100: dang bcas pa legs par bshad pa skabs lnga'i bdag
NG0859:101: nyid can 'di ni bsod nams mngon par 'du byed
NG0859:102: pa'i bdag nyid mi yi dbang mo sa skyong ba
NG0859:103: nyid kyi bka' stsal pa lhur blangs te /
NG0859:104: chos kyi rje kah thog pa'i 'bangs kyi tha shal
NG0859:105: du gyur pa shakya'i btsun pa 'gyur med tshe dbang
NG0859:106: mchog grub nges don bstan 'phel dpal bzang po zhes
NG0859:107: bgyis pas bdag cag gi ston pa kun mkhyen nyi
NG0859:108: ma'i gnyen gzugs sku chos dbyings su bsdus pa'i tshul
NG0859:109: bstan nas bgrang bya nyis stong drug brgya bdun cu
NG0859:110: don brgyad pa me sprul gyi lo dbyug gu zla
NG0859:111: ba'i dkar phyogs kyi rgyal ba gsum pa'i tshes bzang
NG0859:112: por chos dang srid kyi dpal 'byor mngon par mtho
NG0859:113: ba'i lhun grub steng gi rgyal khab chen po nyid
NG0859:114: du sbyar ba 'jig rten kun tu dge legs kyi
NG0859:115: snang ba chen pos khyad par gyur cig / //
